      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The power is managed by a longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal mechanical grip. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, and the suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics for precise turn-in. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS solenoid refresh and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement check. This is a mechanically sound, driver-focused machine that delivers an authentic analog performance experience.",
